<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>769</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 wèi fú yīn wǒ men de xīn jǐn lián zài yī qǐ. wèi fú yīn jiǎo bù zǒu zài yī qǐ.
 ràng měi shuāng jiǎo yìn dōu jiān shí yǒu lì, yǔ zhǔ yī tóng yíng fēng yǔ.
 jǐn guǎn qù sā zhǒng, shén huì ràng tā shēng zhǎng. fù chū de lèi shuǐ, zhǔ dōu kàn zài yǎn lǐ.
 nǐ shòu kǔ, tā hé nǐ tóng shòu kǔ. nǐ yǒu wěi qū, tā hé nǐ tóng kū qì.
 shǐ mìng zài jiān shàng, dōu méi yǒu yóu yù. wèi fú yīn wǒ men de xīn jǐn lián zài yī qǐ.
 jiē guò jì tán de huǒ zhǒng, zài cì fèng xiàn zì jǐ, yī bàng yī bàng de chuán xià qù.</lyrics>
<title>wèi fú yīn 迦南769</title>
</song>